Name: QbQbQb
About the game: Extended soundtrack available CO-OP and single player arcade game. Colorful musical experience designed for both casual and hardcore players. Simple rules and increasing speed makes it an ideal choice if you are looking for a game to occupy your friends, guests or yourself for a while. Each 100 points pumps up the music and gameplay speed. There is also built-in support for color-blind players, gamepads and ... karaoke.
